{"tid":436323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X終於出貨！　首批4.65萬部由鄭州出境 (12:10)","createTime":"2017-10-15T05:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T05:28:56.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9df1e282a8bff14566d313b85f4bee25c7f01fb3","tid":436323,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=AJjNPnWE8cCgUQ5hfbMKxKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e2f34fa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內地傳媒報道，鄭州海關監管首批4.65萬部蘋果公司新手機iPhone X，由鄭州新鄭綜合保稅區發貨，分別從新鄭國際機場和上海浦東國際機場運往荷蘭及阿聯酋。<br />\n<br />\n此前，據台灣產業鏈消息，iPhone X生產良品率略見提升，目前iPhone X每周產量為40萬部，雖仍不算高，但已優於之前的每周10萬部。<br />\n<br />\niPhone X將於10月27日起接受預購，11月3日開始發售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171015/20171015121028fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171015%2F20171015121028fi.html&d=AJjNPnWE8cCgUQ5hfbMKxKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=520e78a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171015/20171015121028fi.html</a><br />\n<br />\n@老貓再世_"}]}